 soundprefs rate
 ŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊ


 Sintassi   : a) soundprefs <modus> rate set <1-2000>
 ŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊŊ b) soundprefs <modus> rate get

